org.svvrl.goal.core.util
Class FSAContainmentOrder

java.lang.Object
  org.svvrl.goal.core.util.FSAContainmentOrder
All Implemented Interfaces:
LatticeListener<FSA>, Order<FSA>
public class FSAContainmentOrder
extends java.lang.Object
implements Order<FSA>, LatticeListener<FSA>

This class defines a partial order for FSA. If this partial order is registered as a lattice listener, to speed up for each insertion into a lattice, the complements of the elements to be inserted will be computed before the insertion and used in deciding the containment relation.

Author:
"Ming-Hsien Tsai"
